snippet.title: Cyberbykes: Shadow Racer VR gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Cyberbykes: Shadow Racer VR, Dos PC game produced by Artificial Software in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/cyberbykes-shadow-racer-vr/7502/
Cyberbike: Shadow Racer VR is a pretty good game, a 3D quite successful. You control a robotic bike remotely and blow up the opposition with 15 different weapons.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
